    "body": "I found what causes the difference between the values shown and the values calculated: MSTORE is marked as \"W_verylow\" in the Yellowpaper (3 gas), shows 3 gas in the remix debugger, but takes up 12 gas on chain. I have released a similar contract on rinkeby, its's the third instruction and pretty obvious: http://rinkeby.etherscan.io/remix?txhash=0xb837a742727706e9b8f57f33477d3b5dfd3959f705f15f041c1ed6357178917b\r\n\r\nI'd be very happy if someone can explain it to me before closing the issue. Thank you.",
